name: Lunar
description:
Lunar (LNR) is a DeFi ecosystem that aims to solve the biggest problems preventing crypto from true mass adoption. The Lunar DEX aims to streamline the entire process of BSC token trading into a single platform with a frictionless user experience.
The Lunar Token (LNR) distributes 3% of LNR transactions and a percentage of Lunar DEX transactions to holders in passive earnings. The ecosystem also includes an NFT collection, Lunar Legion, that receives 0.5% of LNR tx's in passive reflections.
